    <item>
      <title>渣打银行称美元走强有利于日本股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/stronger-dollar-favorable-for-japan-equities-standard-chartered-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打财富管理公司股票策略主管 Daniel Lam 表示，投资者正在为“特朗普获胜的可能性更大”做准备，这意味着美元兑日元将在短期内走高。Lam 认为，这对日本股市有利。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/stronger-dollar-favorable-for-japan-equities-standard-chartered-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:53:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行准备通过银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/china-central-bank-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行表示，目前已通过与贷方达成的协议，拥有“数千亿”人民币国债可供使用，央行旨在为创纪录的涨势降温。彭博电视台的吉尔·迪西斯报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/china-central-bank-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管全球股市创下新高，比特币仍连续第四天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币连续第四个交易日下跌，这是加密货币更大范围抛售的一部分，与近期全球股市创下的历史新高形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行准备通过各大银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行采取了进一步措施，通过出售国债来冷却创纪录的股市上涨，并表示，目前通过与贷款机构达成的协议，央行可以持有“数千亿元”人民币的国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者预期美联储将开始放松政策，黄金价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储将在年底前降息，黄金价格连续两周上涨，交易员们正在关注美国非农就业数据，以寻找下一批经济前景的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风风险和美国库存下降导致油价接近两个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风贝丽尔预示着风暴季节可能会更加糟糕，而美国原油库存减少暗示需求增加，油价交易价格接近两个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
